290
00:18:47.040 --> 00:18:47.963
Fast.

291
00:18:51.250 --> 00:18:52.563
They have to do something.

292
00:18:53.640 --> 00:18:56.400
- Yeah. but Mr. Soto?

293
00:18:56.400 --> 00:18:57.233
