310
00:19:58.873 --> 00:19:59.706
- I will.

311
00:20:04.391 --> 00:20:06.974
(gun cranking)

312
00:20:14.130 --> 00:20:16.173
- Just be safe.

313
00:20:20.710 --> 00:20:21.543
- Thank you.

314
00:20:26.991 --> 00:20:29.658
(Felix sighing)

315
00:20:32.400 --> 00:20:33.233
Stand. son.

316
00:20:34.250 --> 00:20:36.950
