598
00:38:26.808 --> 00:38:29.391
(woman crying)

599
00:38:31.639 --> 00:38:32.472
- Mother?

600
00:38:36.969 --> 00:38:38.473
The doors!

601
00:38:38.473 --> 00:38:41.140
(intense music)

602
00:38:44.734 --> 00:38:47.984
