00:44:15.720 --> 00:44:18.830
- I wish those adults
listened to you more. sir.

676
00:44:18.830 --> 00:44:20.373
- You and me both. kiddo.

677
00:44:21.990 --> 00:44:22.823
- Thanks.

678
00:44:25.230 --> 00:44:26.130
- You and me both.

