754
00:47:50.900 --> 00:47:52.780
that I intend to keep.

755
00:47:52.780 --> 00:47:55.500
- But I can go. Aunt Martha.

756
00:47:55.500 --> 00:47:56.903
I saw the balloon.

757
00:47:59.290 --> 00:48:01.380
I wanna help for once.

758
00:48:01.380 --> 00:48:05.840
